{"tid":2449332,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（改歌） 連登人若變 (再版)","createTime":"2021-03-16T14:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T09:51:05.000Z","uid":307910,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5072d77f889ffc70caec4af19301d3973989d051","tid":2449332,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"連登嘅人若變 這夜有心事<br />\n想起舊愛kelly還掛念<br />\n但不夠迷人在記抑裏面<br />\n只知道人若變不想講再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登嘅人若變 好掛住kelly<br />\nLIHK(g) 抒發感情才是意義<br />\n句子過分無奈最為簡單的暗示<br />\nKelly, 我真係好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n渾噩到晚上 獨個坐在床<br />\n間房裏籠罩酸縮 是J 你的感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本她 都不會欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登嘅人若變 晚上就出現<br />\n上lin登感情台訴說心事<br />\n留言班仆街說佢鬧得好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部負面 被狙擊很多遍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但同場有一位絲打友善的留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n把聲好聽 也不怕和我通電<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加有Kelly氣質模糊記抑交纏<br />\n通了兩電 就忘記Kelly<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就快忘記kelly<br />\nJ下你把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你說只有最愛才能掂你妹妹<br />\n有晚卻被逼和毒撚做愛<span class=\"x-small\">（我）</span><br />\n<br />\n連登嘅人若變 這夜有心事<br />\n不知跟她何能再見面<br />\n和她相識十載卻認不出聲線<br />\n寫了句句lin登出post後入眠<br />\n<br />\n偷偷叫著這春幻想她看見<br />\n留言回覆是知還是不發現<br />\n再見不到卻淪成隔空對電<br />\n人若變和kelly LIHK(g)聊天"},{"pid":"f7faa153e60dc54d1eec35e1e784e903285764b6","tid":2449332,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"少少尷尬..."},{"pid":"420869ddc06bb83d711d1c7eb2b66e094582a9ef","tid":2449332,"uid":218575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"算啦 唔想呃你 <br />\n係好撚尷尬.."},{"pid":"efee08d98d15fd26d4d74c46b4b53dac9c5f9c98","tid":2449332,"uid":307910,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"一直以來都無好好解釋過首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次想利用下呢個機會<br />\n<br />\n呢首歌係講，人若變同kelly分左手之後，日日都好唔開心，日日都上連登叫春，但係比感情台嘅人冷言恥笑，但有一日卻遇到一個身份神秘嘅靚聲絲打，講咗幾個電話就迷上咗呢個陌生嘅女仔<br />\n<br />\n去到有一次佢講起自己嘅感情經歷，人若變先發現呢個女仔好似一個好熟悉嘅人，當嗰位絲打提起自己有同過毒撚一齊嘅慘痛經歷之後，先發現電話對面呢個係識咗十年嘅kelly, 但就因訊號同語氣嘅影響，令佢發現唔到呢個素未謀面嘅女絲打就係kelly本人<br />\n<br />\n佢同kelly依然間唔中傾下電話咁，但卻知道同對方無論用咩身份都唔可能再見面，只好繼續喺連登繼續出post, 希望kelly自己意識到人若變嘅身份，但一方面又好怕佢知道咗就以後唔會再見面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec611267b4332e38def8ab89eab37753bf695d8","tid":2449332,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7faa153e60dc54d1eec35e1e784e903285764b6","tid":2449332,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"少少尷尬..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"呢首歌好耐之前作..."},{"pid":"2aa21999534fee6208fc42d43afe3aa18e044a08","tid":2449332,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"420869ddc06bb83d711d1c7eb2b66e094582a9ef","tid":2449332,"uid":218575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"算啦 唔想呃你 <br />\n係好撚尷尬.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"好彩你唔係kelly<br />\n如果係kelly一定會鍾意呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79a70c57d162cda52f38404d3beab2ada459820","tid":2449332,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efee08d98d15fd26d4d74c46b4b53dac9c5f9c98","tid":2449332,"uid":307910,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"一直以來都無好好解釋過首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/w